The hot springs occur along and at the base of the west valley wall in a 3 km long zone that extends southwest from Hot Springs Bay (fig. 27).
The thermal waters issue from fissures in hydrothermally cemented stream bank sediments, from pools in valley alluvium, and through beach sands in Spring the intertidal zone near the mouth of the Hot Springs Creek.
